{"tid":2077272,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"大衛路爾斯續約1年","createTime":"2020-06-24T07:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T12:09:17.000Z","uid":72497,"like":30,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"e676bdc0052e7976a588c06ea845af929615d728","tid":2077272,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:07:26.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴與「自殺式」中堅大衛路爾斯續約1年。<br />\n阿仙奴領隊阿迪達真是勇氣可嘉，周二竟然與巴西中堅大衛路爾斯（David Luiz）續約1年，周薪12萬英鎊。這名33歲球星合約至6月30日屆滿，之前一直希望續約兩年，但如今已接受球隊的1年新約。 大衛路爾斯長期表現反覆，復賽首仗對曼城，後備上陣26分鐘，獨力改變比賽的戰局，炮製兩個失誤導致輸兩球，還領到紅牌出場。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，大衛路爾斯賽後向球隊道歉，外界都認定他將不會獲得續約。 同日獲得一紙新合約的，還有修咸頓借將蘇亞利斯，他加盟以來一直受傷從未出場，但也正式以1400萬英鎊加盟。不過，法國中場根度斯近期捲入侮辱對手醜聞，則很可能在今夏被出售。"},{"pid":"8d8137dae4f3acf5e2d2ca8f73397ebee5441eb2","tid":2077272,"uid":72497,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:11:54.000Z","msg":"阿狗真係無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f8297a89b10306cd19fc3ab6171a7bb8808cf8","tid":2077272,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:13:21.000Z","msg":"好 繼續有笑片睇"},{"pid":"c7b9e21b40f8d20690ea2aa60ec7e2fcd3e7569e","tid":2077272,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:15:16.000Z","msg":"垃圾都有得續<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54d1ed7b7eba0a5f7bcff863239e78ba429d6f0","tid":2077272,"uid":72497,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"c7b9e21b40f8d20690ea2aa60ec7e2fcd3e7569e","tid":2077272,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:15:16.000Z","msg":"垃圾都有得續<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:16:01.000Z","msg":"球會icon 嚟"},{"pid":"95d05056ee9c85aced37aea812b7a8d98f41b5f9","tid":2077272,"uid":15830,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:20:15.000Z","msg":"續黎洗廁所？"},{"pid":"d5194f507ed7182beae1f4f96cf35074a6a6d365","tid":2077272,"uid